  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4  \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd : \u0bb2\u0bbe\u0b83\u0baa\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gas cylinders lined up in front of the vacant lot: Laugh distribution - Litro cylinders lined up",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Laugh Gas Company has been distributing gas cylinders to people who have been waiting for cylinders for the past one week in front of the empty cricket ground.",
        "In this context, Laugfs has distributed gas cylinders ahead of Sri Lanka's Test series against Australia starting tomorrow (29).",
        "For more than a week now, people in the area have been queuing up around the empty cricket ground to get their cylinders.",
        "However, people have been waiting in line for about a month, but Litro Gas has not yet delivered the gas cylinders, people said.",
        "As a result, people waiting for gas have said that empty litro gas cylinders will be lined up outside the cricket ground during tomorrow's cricket match."
      ],
